Package rubank

Class MoneyMarket

java.lang.Object
pizzapizza.Account
pizzapizza.Savings
pizzapizza.MoneyMarket
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Account>
public class MoneyMarket extends Savings
The MoneyMarket class represents a MoneyMarket account at RU Bank, and it inherits the Savings class. Overrides the monthlyInterest() and monthlyFee() methods from the Savings class
Author:
Sibi suriyanarayan Tiruchirapalli venketaramani, Rahulraj Rajesh
